OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPost Office scandal victims
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fset to be cleared by law   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Hundreds of people wrongly convicted in
OL,6, the Post Office scandal are set to have
OL,7, their names cleared under new          
OL,8, legislation planned by the government. 
OL,10,FThe law is expected to come into effect
OL,11,Fby the end of July and will apply to   
OL,12,Fconvictions in England and Wales.      
OL,14,FIt will apply to convictions meeting   
OL,15,Fspecific criteria and is expected to   
OL,16,Fclear the majority of victims.         
OL,18,FThe government said the possible       
OL,19,Fexoneration of some genuinely guilty of
OL,20,Fcrimes was "a price worth paying".     
